Apple just announced the iPhone 17 lineup, the new iPhone Air, and AirPods Pro 3. Linus and Luke discuss the big changes like 120Hz on the base iPhone, 256GB starting storage, titanium vs aluminum marketing, and why the iPhone Air is already polarizing. They also dive into the AirPods Pro 3 upgrades, Apple’s odd accessory choices, and what’s missing from this year’s lineup.
